room_title: Escape room "Missing Starlet" by Hysterium Escapes in Fort Wayne
review: Our group of 3 had so much fun in the Missing Starlet Room!! Our minds were definitely tested and we laughed the whole time! Thanks for an awesome night! We will absolutely be returning!

room_title: Escape room "Missing Starlet" by Hysterium Escapes in Fort Wayne
review: We experienced the Starlet Room last night. It was well thought out, full of nice touches. Our game master (John) was a lot of fun! This was our tenth room, and I must say we were very impressed with every aspect of the experience.We will definitely be checking in again to try the serial killer room.
